              Why Gladiator Games Gift&nbsp;Cards?
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-brand-gray">
              Better than another game they might not play. Give them unlimited access to 100+&nbsp;games.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-12">
            <div class="card text-center">
              <div class="bg-brand-orange/20 rounded-full p-4 w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
                <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-brand-orange" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-white mb-3">Great Value</h3>
              <p class="text-brand-gray">
                Yearly memberships save 2 months. 12 months for the price of&nbsp;10!
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="card text-center">
